OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud but a
OL,6,Fgenerally dry, bright and rather warm
OL,7,Fday. Cloud increasing late afternoon
OL,8,Fperhaps bringing some light rain into
OL,9,Fthe far west by early evening. Locally
OL,10,Fbreezy during the afternoon, otherwise
OL,11,Fwinds generally .
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning cloudy across all
OL,14,Fparts through the evening with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain
OL,16,Fspreading east overnight. Chance of
OL,17,Fisolated heavier bursts of rain in the
OL,18,Ffar west after dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
