OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloudy at first, some
OL,6,Fintermittent rain in places. More
OL,7,Fpersistent rain, with embedded heavier
OL,8,Fpulses, spreads east during the day,
OL,9,Ffollowed by brighter conditions and
OL,10,Fscattered, possibly thundery showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FSunshine and showers Tuesday and
OL,14,FWednesday with a risk of hail and
OL,15,Fthunder. A fine start likely on
OL,16,FThursday, then rain arriving later.
OL,17,FBreezy at times and rather cool
OL,18,Foverall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
